column3: None shall pass through the Gates of Judgement who have not been granted leave to do so.
In order to enter Ishgard, you must first meet the following requirements:
You must have registered a product key for FINAL FANTASY XIV: Heavensward to your service account.
You must have completed the main scenario quest \xe2\x80\x9cBefore the Dawn.\xe2\x80\x9d
You must be currently undertaking the quest \xe2\x80\x9cComing to Ishgard.\xe2\x80\x9d
To review your quest progression, select \x02\x13\x06\xfe\xff\xff{\x1a\x03Duty\x02\x13\x02\xec\x03 from the main menu, followed by \x02\x13\x06\xfe\xff\xff{\x1a\x03Journal\x02\x13\x02\xec\x03.
